id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section1" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>1.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=determine-if-this-is-the-right-business-for-you>Determine if this is the right business for you.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section1-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>1.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=assess-your-skills-and-social-media-marketing-knowledge>Assess your skills and social media marketing knowledge.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-assess-your-skills-and-social-media-marketing-knowledge-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Assess your skills and social media marketing knowledge."></div></div><p>While the need for social media managers is growing, the field is relatively new and as with any business, you need to determine if you're capable of performing the job. The requirements expected from this role include copywriting skills, relevant experience, and solid knowledge of SEO practices.</p><p><strong>Do you have an understanding of social media as a marketing tool?</strong> Social media differs from other forms of marketing in the sense that it is about having an informative and entertaining conversation with your clients' following. Each platform is unique, and how you promote a client on LinkedIn differs vastly from how you do it on Facebook.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>In this industry, you need to have your finger on the pulse of different social media platforms' changes in policies and algorithms at all times.</p></div><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>You need to be able to convey each client's unique voice in their social media posts, for instance, some businesses may choose to have a serious and professional social media presence, while others choose to be lighthearted and quirky.</p></div><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>You need to work together with your clients to make them understand that social media marketing is about building loyalty and trust, not about making sales. Once you achieve this, you need to develop a plan for them.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section1-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>1.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=consider-the-pros-and-cons>Consider the pros and cons.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-consider-the-pros-and-cons-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Consider the pros and cons."></div></div><p>One of the main benefits of starting a social media marketing agency is low startup costs. In this role, you won't need to immediately hire staff, you can work from anywhere, and most social media platforms are inexpensive.</p><p>On the other hand, some notable cons include the fact that many traditional business owners don't see the significance of social media marketing and you will need to manage multiple social media accounts at a time.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section2" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>2.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=choose-the-services-your-social-media-marketing-agency-will-offer>Choose the services your social media marketing agency will offer.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section2-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>2.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=start-with-the-basics>Start with the basics.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-start-with-the-basics-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Start with the basics."></div></div><p>The early stages of your business will require hard work and most of that will be the responsibility of one or two employees, depending on how small your team is. During this time, it's best to start small and only offer basic services that are manageable on a daily basis. This way you can start building your skills to eventually start managing multiple clients.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Think about offering start-up and/or full-service packages. <strong>Start-up services</strong> create social media accounts for clients and then pass the management back to them. If you offer <strong>full-service packages</strong>, you create accounts, post content, and moderate communities. It is good to offer a combination of services and a range of packages to cater to various clients' needs.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section2-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>2.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=decide-what-industry-you-want-to-focus-on>Decide what industry you want to focus on.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-decide-what-industry-you-want-to-focus-on-288x288-20200729.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Decide what industry you want to focus on."></div></div><p>As a small business, it may be wise to focus on a niche market. For instance lawyers, doctors, or dentists offices. This could also help your business grow within that specific industry.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section2-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>2.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=establish-which-platforms-you-are-going-to-focus-on>Establish which platforms you are going to focus on.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-establish-which-social-media-platforms-you-want-to-focus-on-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Establish which platforms you are going to focus on."></div></div><p>It is important to know all the major platforms, but it is good to focus on those that drive results in the industry you are focusing on.</p><p><strong>Popular social media platforms for businesses:</strong></p><ul><li>Facebook.</li><li>LinkedIn.</li><li>X formerly known as Twitter.</li><li>YouTube.</li><li>Instagram.</li><li>TikTok.</li></ul></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section3" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>3.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=conduct-market-research>Conduct market research.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section3-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>3.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=establish-if-your-business-concept-is-feasible>Establish if your business concept is feasible.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-conduct-market-research-4193x2785-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Establish if your business concept is feasible."></div></div><p>Will enough people with enough spending power use your services? Who is your prospective client? Doing market research for your social media marketing business shows who your clients are, reveals if there are enough of them, and establishes how best to make them happy.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section3-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>3.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=determine-if-you-can-meet-customer-requirements>Determine if you can meet customer requirements.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-determine-if-you-are-able-to-meet-customer-requirements-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Determine if you can meet customer requirements."></div></div><p>Evaluate if you will be able to meet your prospective clients' social media marketing needs. If not, consider reworking your concept to ensure it is in line with your potential clients' requirements.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section3-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>3.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=follow-social-media-marketers-influencers-and-advocate-marketers>Follow social media marketers, influencers, and advocate marketers.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-follow-competition-online-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Follow social media marketers, influencers, and advocate marketers."></div></div><p>The best way to learn is by studying the competition and other social media professionals. Don't underestimate what you can learn from your competition.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section3-step4" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>3.4&nbsp;</span><h4 id=get-accurate-facts-figures-and-statistics>Get accurate facts, figures, and statistics.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-get-accurate-facts-and-figures-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Get accurate facts, figures, and statistics."></div></div><p>You could hire a professional market research firm or you can teach yourself to do market research, and use data analytics tools. There are free options available if you don’t want to spend money on these tools.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section4" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>4.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=make-a-detailed-list-of-what-you-need>Make a detailed list of what you need.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section4-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>4.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=consider-your-startup-requirements>Consider your startup requirements.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-make-a-list-of-what-you-need-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Consider your startup requirements."></div></div><p>To get a clear idea of what it is going to cost you to get your social media marketing agency up and running, you need to make a detailed list of what you will need. A key benefit of starting a social media marketing agency is its minimal start-up requirements.</p><p><strong>What you need to start a social media marketing business:</strong></p><ul><li>Online course. Invest in an online course to learn more about social media and digital marketing, which could benefit you as a refresher even if you are knowledgeable in this area.</li><li>Reliable computer, phone, and internet access.</li><li>A social media following and influence. You need a large number of followers that engage with your posts by commenting, and liking or sharing them.</li></ul></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section4-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>4.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=calculate-your-startup-costs>Calculate your startup costs.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-calculate-your-start-up-costs-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Calculate your startup costs."></div></div><p>According to our research, it costs between $1,410.00 and $2,575.00 to start a social marketing manager agency.</p><p><strong>Startup costs to consider:</strong></p><ul><li>Social media marketing agency course: $30.00 to $700.00</li><li>Smartphone: $800.00</li><li>Laptop or computer: $500.00</li><li>Business formation costs: $30.00 to $500.00.</li><li>Internet services: $50.00 to $75.00 per month.</li></ul></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section5" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>5.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=create-a-business-plan>Create a business plan.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section5-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>5.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=consider-the-research-you-conducted-and-showcase-it-in-your-business-plan>Consider the research you conducted and showcase it in your business plan.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-create-a-detailed-business-plan-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Consider the research you conducted and showcase it in your business plan."></div></div><p>Once you have a clear picture of the social media marketing agency you want to start, you can create a business plan. During this process, you will be asked to present your business plan to potential investors, banks, and partners. Therefore, it's important that your business plan is well-researched and compelling.</p><p><strong>Essentials for a Social Media Marketing Agency Business Plan:</strong></p><ul><li>Executive summary.</li><li>Company description.</li><li>Products and services.</li><li>Marketing plan.</li><li>Operational plan.</li><li>Management.</li><li>Ownership's personal financial statements.</li><li>Financial plan.</li><li>Appendices.</li></ul></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section6" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>6.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=choose-a-business-name>Choose a business name.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section6-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=think-about-your-brand-and-services>Think about your brand and services.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-think-about-your-brand-and-services-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Think about your brand and services."></div></div><p>Your social media marketing company's name will become your brand, and it needs to be relevant to your service and your market.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>You can either choose to come up with the name yourself or you can use a business name generator like <a
href="https://www.namesnack.com/">NameSnack</a>, an online-based platform that uses AI technology to generate thousands of names.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section6-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=perform-a-trademark-search>Perform a trademark search.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-search-the-usptos-trademark-database-288x288-20200703.png?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Perform a trademark search."></div></div><p>When you have a couple of business names in mind, write a list of potential business names and <a
href="https://www.namesnack.com/guides/how-to-trademark-a-name">conduct a trademark search</a> with the <a
href="https://www.uspto.gov/">U.S. Patent and Trademark Office</a> to ensure your name is available for use.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section6-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=perform-a-name-availability-search-with-the-state>Perform a name availability search with the state.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-search-the-sosdirect-288x288-20200619_2023-09-27-011644_apxl.png?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Perform a name availability search with the state."></div></div><p>Once you've confirmed that your business is available with the U.S. Patent and Trademark Office, you have to <a
href="https://www.namesnack.com/guides/how-to-check-if-a-business-name-is-available-for-free">check with your local state department</a> to verify if the name has already been registered. If not, you can trademark your business name and register it will the state department.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section7" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>7.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=form-your-social-media-marketing-company>Form your social media marketing company.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section7-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=choose-a-business-entity>Choose a business entity.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-form-a-business-288x288-20200728_2023-09-27-011745_tytc.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Choose a business entity."></div></div><p>You have the choice of registering your business as a corporation, sole proprietorship, partnership, or Limited Liability Company (LLC). Because your business will likely not require a corporate office or shareholders, we recommend starting out with a sole proprietorship, which may not require official registration.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section7-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=get-an-employer-identification-number>Get an Employer Identification Number (EIN).</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-irs-ein-application-288x288-20200624_2023-09-27-011834_xptp.png?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Get an Employer Identification Number (EIN)."></div></div><p>This option is a must if you plan on hiring additional employees. You can register for an EIN on the <a
href="https://www.irs.gov/businesses/small-businesses-self-employed/apply-for-an-employer-identification-number-ein-online">IRS website</a>.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section7-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=open-a-business-bank-account>Open a business bank account.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-open-bank-account-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Open a business bank account."></div></div><p>To ensure your personal and business finances remain separate, consider opening a business bank account. This is a great way to establish credibility, obtain accurate statements, and benefit from business perks.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section7-step4" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.4&nbsp;</span><h4 id=apply-for-licenses-and-permits>Apply for licenses and permits.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-apply-for-license-and-permits-288x288-20200729_2023-09-27-012008_vnyn.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Apply for licenses and permits."></div></div><p>To legally operate your business, you may require additional legal permits or licenses. However, this could largely depend on your location and its local requirements.</p><p>In most states and counties you won't require a special license to start a social media marketing business. You would need a general business license when you officially start your business, though. Go to the Small Business Administration (SBA) site to check for <a
href="https://www.sba.gov/business-guide/launch-your-business/apply-licenses-permits">state licenses and permits</a> you may need.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section8" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>8.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=get-funding>Get funding.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section8-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=ask-family-and-friends>Ask family and friends.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-ask-friends-and-family-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Ask family and friends."></div></div><p>One of the more common options is asking family and friends to invest in your business. Prepare a well-informed presentation and include your business plan.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section8-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=apply-for-a-loan-with-the-small-business-administration>Apply for a loan with the Small Business Administration (SBA).</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-apply-for-an-sba-loan-288x288-20200724_2023-09-27-012220_vepr.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Apply for a loan with the Small Business Administration (SBA)."></div></div><p>Managed by the SBA, these loans help businesses with limited financial alternatives to access funding at low-interest rates through federally-backed lending.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section8-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=apply-for-a-small-business-loan>Apply for a small business loan.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-apply-for-a-small-business-loan-288x288-20200728_2023-09-27-012325_zvcs.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Apply for a small business loan."></div></div><p>Small business lending includes microloans, bank loans, credit cards, venture capital, and SBA-backed loans. Your social media marketing agency can use a small business loan to purchase equipment and more.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section8-step4" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.4&nbsp;</span><h4 id=get-a-business-credit-card>Get a business credit card.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-apply-for-a-business-credit-card-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Get a business credit card."></div></div><p>If your business is less than two-years-old and you have a good credit record, your chances of qualifying for a business credit card are good. A business credit card is great for small expenses that need to be handled immediately.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section9" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
