class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>9.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=offer-a-free-audit>Offer a free audit.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-offer-a-free-audit-288x288-20200728.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Offer a free audit."></div></div><p>A great way to attract clients is by offering them <strong>a free digital audit to show them an overview of their current online efforts</strong> and how you can help them improve. Include relevant data and analytics that details their current online presence and their potential brand development if they use your services.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section9-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>9.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=create-a-company-website>Create a company website.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-create-a-company-website-288x288-20200728_2023-09-27-012836_grut.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Create a company website."></div></div><p>List all relevant information customers may be interested in, such as prices, services, and contact information. If possible, include testimonials from previous clients.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section10" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>10.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=hire-employees>Hire employees.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-agency-section10-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>10.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=decide-if-you-need-to-hire-employees>Decide if you need to hire employees.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-decide-if-you-need-to-hire-additional-employees-288x288-20200723_2023-09-27-012938_mlmc.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Decide if you need to hire employees."></div></div><p>When starting out, it's not recommended to hire a team of employees. It's best to first establish a solid client base and grow your business. However, as your social media marketing agency grows you may need a personal or virtual assistant, an accountant, and multiple account managers.</p><div
class="step-direction">
