class="section-faq"><div
class="container"><h2 id=fAQs class="section-heading">FAQs:</h2><div
class="row"><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-much-does-it-cost-to-start-a-social-media-marketing-business class="question">How much does it cost to start a social media marketing business?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>It costs between $1,410.00 and $2,575.00 to start a social marketing management agency.</p></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-much-does-a-social-media-marketing-manager-make class="question">How much does a social media marketing manager make?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>Our research found social media managers make around $15.52 per hour, and an average of $49,390 per year.</p></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-much-should-i-charge-for-social-media-consulting class="question">How much should I charge for social media consulting?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>It depends on your experience, and referrals and testimonials will help you to earn more. Our research found social media consultants charge anywhere from $15.00 to $250.00 per hour, and even more. The average cost for digital marketing services ranges from $2,500 to $12,000 per month for SMBs.</p></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-do-i-calculate-an-hourly-rate-for-consulting class="question">How do I calculate an hourly rate for consulting?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>Decide what salary you would like to make, divide it by the number of working weeks in a year, and then by 40 for your number of working hours per week. Mark that number up by 25% to 50%.</p></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-do-i-get-my-first-social-media-marketing-clients class="question">How do I get my first social media marketing clients?</h3><div
class="answer"><ul><li>Network, and approach your existing contacts.</li><li>Offer your services for free, and ask for referrals.</li><li>Set up a landing page and promote it.</li><li>Do email marketing or make cold calls.</li><li>Keep an eye on job boards and freelancing sites.</li></ul></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-do-i-convince-clients-to-use-social-media-marketing-services class="question">How do I convince clients to use social media marketing services?</h3><div
class="answer"><ul><li>Point out that social media marketing attracts traffic that turns into leads.</li><li>Explain to them that you are giving them access to a valuable customer service tool.</li><li>Make them aware that your services free up time for them to grow their business in other ways.</li><li>Tell them that their following may spread their message to their own contacts.</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div> <script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How much does it cost to start a social media marketing business?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<p>It costs between $1,410.00 and $2,575.00 to start a social marketing management agency.<\/p>\n"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How much does a social media marketing manager make?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<p>Our research found social media managers make around $15.52 per hour, and an average of $49,390 per year.<\/p>\n"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How much should I charge for social media consulting?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<p>It depends on your experience, and referrals and testimonials will help you to earn more. Our research found social media consultants charge anywhere from $15.00 to $250.00 per hour, and even more. The average cost for digital marketing services ranges from $2,500 to $12,000 per month for SMBs.<\/p>\n"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I calculate an hourly rate for consulting?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<p>Decide what salary you would like to make, divide it by the number of working weeks in a year, and then by 40 for your number of working hours per week. Mark that number up by 25% to 50%.<\/p>\n"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I get my first social media marketing clients?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<ul>\n<li>Network, and approach your existing contacts.<\/li>\n<li>Offer your services for free, and ask for 